==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stilly
<hw>Still"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Still; quiet;
calm.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>stilly</qex> hour when storms are gone.</q>
<rj><qau>Moore.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stilly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Stilly
<hw>Stil"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a still manner;
quietly; silently; softly.</def> <rj><au>Dr. H. More.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The hum of either army <qex>stilly</qex> sounds.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stilpnomelane</ent>⟦br⟧
